---
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#050706] py-24 font-sans selection:bg-green-500/30 selection:text-white">
  
  <!-- Centrirano prigušeno belo svetlo u pozadini -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 h-[500px] w-[500px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.015] blur-[120px] pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-green-400">// Trust & Compliance</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Zero Risk. Complete Liability Coverage.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Guard 1 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/60 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-lg font-mono text-green-400 font-bold">// 01</div>
        <h4 class="mt-3 text-base font-bold text-white">Verified General Liability</h4>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
          Every contractor on our platform undergoes active screening for up-to-date insurance coverage to protect your entire asset value.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Guard 2 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/60 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-lg font-mono text-green-400 font-bold">// 02</div>
        <h4 class="mt-3 text-base font-bold text-white">Workers' Comp Enforced</h4>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
          Zero homeowner liability. We explicitly filter networks to ensure crew members are fully covered on-site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Guard 3 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-900 bg-zinc-950/60 p-6 backdrop-blur-sm sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="text-lg font-mono text-green-400 font-bold">// 03</div>
        <h4 class="mt-3 text-base font-bold text-white">Local County Compliance</h4>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
          All routed partners hold current arboricultural licenses matching South Florida's municipal structural safety laws.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>